- One, two, three.

650
01:32:20,953 --> 01:32:22,705
-天哪 那张脸真难看
- God, that's an ugly face.

651
01:32:24,832 --> 01:32:25,791
来吧
Come.

652
01:32:26,792 --> 01:32:28,002
我需要你的帮助
I need your help.

653
01:32:45,770 --> 01:32:46,896
-怎么了？
- What's wrong?

654
01:32:53,069 --> 01:32:55,488
她不会被杀的
She can't be killed.

655
01:32:56,322 --> 01:32:57,823
她会回来的
She'll come back.

